div.div: Dungeon Meshi: Senshi no Kantan Cooking!

Stop-motion short in honor of the 5th tankoubon going on sale. It features Senshi's hands trying to prepare a walking mushroom. It is the same walking mushroom as shown in the manga's 1st volume in the "Monster Tidbits" bonus chapter.
The second season of Princess Connect! Re:Dive.

Gorou is a gynecologist and idol fan whos in shock after his favorite star, Ai, announces an impromptu hiatus. Little does Gorou realize that hes about to forge a bond with her that defies all common sense! Lies are an idols weapon! (Source: Yen Press) Notes: - Nominated for the 14th and 15th Manga Taisho. - Nominated for the 26th Tezuka Osamu Cultural Prize. - Nominated for the 67th Shogakukan Manga Award in the general category. - Nominated for the 46th Kodansha Manga Award. - Winner of the 7th Next Manga Award in the print category. - Chapter count includes 2 extra chapters.
Akutou Ikka no Manamusume, Tenseisaki mo Otome Game no Gokudou Reijoudeshita.: Saijoukyuu Ranku no Akuyaku-sama, sono Dekiai wa Fuyoudesu! @COMIC

After her sudden death at the hands of an assassin, the former granddaughter of a yakuza boss reincarnates in an otome game as the heroine. The game is, of course, set in the time of early European mafia (but with magic), specifically a kingdom where the royal family is supported behind the scenes by five major gangsters!

A dangerous love game between a former yakuza heiress and her villain fianc begins!

(Source: TO Books, translated)
